data.description: WELCOME HOME! Your new home is very conveniently located, close to major highways, shopping and dining venues. This home features an open floor plan, which creates a smooth flow between the kitchen, dining and living rooms. Your kitchen is a great work space, with gas cooking and stainless steel appliances. Upstairs features include 2 master bedrooms, one with a over-sized mud-set shower & dual vanities, the other a perfect room for visiting guests or that young adult in your family. See this home today!
